<br>
&quot;Well,&quot; grumbles Mildikin.  &quot;That's a laugh only a mother could love.&quot;<br>
<br>
Katreena nods at the remark, and the entire lot of use were obviously nervous.  &quot;Her's the deal, gang.&quot; Mildikin starts. &quot;We either wait out the night and give that witch a chance to cause more trouble, or we prepare to high tail it while those of you that follow religion pray we make it though alive.&quot;  Kelee nods and states as she pulls out her drum, &quot;The safes route would be to run along the edge of the forest past Rivervale's enterence.&quot;  Mildikin nods in agreement.  Chantrelle says wearily, &quot;So, are we ready?&quot;<br>
<br>
