With the ache in my shoulder growing stronger and my body feeling weaker and weaker. I start so shiver as I turn to walk back to the other, feeling cold and hot at the same time. In a weak voice, I whisper to the frist waiting in Highpass for me &quot;Khaldron...&quot;<br>
