<br>
&quot;Why hello young elf!&quot;  Said the inn keeper as Eldoren walked through the door holding his nose.  &quot;Where have you traveled from son?&quot;  asked the inn keeper.<br>
<br>
&quot;From the Faydark, sir.&quot; said Eldoren still trying to catch his breath from the stench of Freeport.  &quot;Where am I anyway?&quot; asked Eldoren.<br>
<br>
&quot;Well shaw, you're in the East Commonlands son!&quot;  said the inn keeper.  &quot;How could you not know that?&quot;<br>
<br>
