Off in Lavastorm, Lady Kuvanu at the side of Lord Rashek says &quot;what information comes from our daughter Molina?&quot; &quot;The link was cut short, my dear, something must be wrong, we must get to our family and help them. Evil is stalking us and we need to be united&quot;.<br>
